Busy busy busy! So many people being served and a terrific atmosphere. Food was abundant, fresh and tasty. Lots of variety but of course the signature dish of Peking Duck is the speciality.
We had a private room for 20 of us, the service was great and the food super, well worth going to this restaurant.
